{"tid":438542,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"原來預訂由步院之森唔係想像咁難","createTime":"2017-10-17T04:15:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T13:36:09.000Z","uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"3914550f34a61e02f7cb66cd6c3999b8139b74ac","tid":438542,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T04:15:48.000Z","msg":"之前好多人都話由步院之森易 full 難 book，自已本應下個月 7 號搭，列車要早一個月開售，但搬屋忙到完全冇左件事，到尋日先醒起要訂車票，向九洲 jr join 會員跟著睇當日由步院之森班次，08:45 發 13:35 著，而且揀位方面大把位揀，我仲可以揀到車頭位，唔知係咪因為之前天災改道後要兜成五粒鐘先到所以冇咁多人坐，剩係諗到要坐足五粒鐘真係人都癲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cab72e2d3bc22161e574d37b513ae841adaa922","tid":438542,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T04:19:02.000Z","msg":"搭巴士la......."},{"pid":"b288e5d72440659f1cb38ea97fb8c24bb16a5945","tid":438542,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T04:21:53.000Z","msg":"咁你仲搭?"},{"pid":"7e3b3a79864bb457583243ac6c4fd35e4d390768","tid":438542,"uid":5218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T04:23:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁你仲搭?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為不嬲都好想坐一次。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"563f6b3bd13f84e18d438e05b68fea8644c6c54f","tid":438542,"uid":38143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T04:24:17.000Z","msg":"其實難係難在用pass walk in 劃位啫..."},{"pid":"6ffeca5d8efaae9f0a686b90fcf8667ca696bafa","tid":438542,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T04:24:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭巴士la.......</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係乜野路線？"},{"pid":"deaf72997246c852d26fbfc32c7accd15a14ccab","tid":438542,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T04:26:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實難係難在用pass walk in 劃位啫...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇買 pass，我只係搭一程，之後向由步院去阿蘇，諗緊租觀光的去。"},{"pid":"c82a6bf33f5278f188626995ed4f19f01946e249","tid":438542,"ui